				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Notice something subtle.\n\nWe are not using UUIDs.\n\nWe introduce another abstraction.\n\nPartyId\n\ninstead of\n\nUUID\n\nWhy?\n\nBecause UUID is an implementation.\n\nParty identity is a business concept.\n\nOne day identities might come from\n\na passport\na tax number\nan ERP\na graph database\nan external registry\n\nNone of those should leak into Party."
